                                                   India, Australia polo tie
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: The Indiabulls group will host a polo international match between India and Australia on Saturday at the ARC Polo Ground in Mumbai.         
	According to information reaching here, the best Indian and Australian players will be seen in action for the first time on Mumbai turf.         
	The event will also include a fashion show and a dare devil trick riding display by the 61st Cavalry.                                                                                                                       
